
To install mpi4py enter the below command
    sudo apt-get install python

Next
    sudo apt-get install python-mpi4py
    
Make a directory 
    mkdir name
    
Create a machine file witht the ip addresses of master and client nodes

Install numpy
    sudo apt-get install numpy

Create your program file

Run the program using:

mpirun.openmpi -np 2 -machinefile /home/mpi/mpi4py/machinefile python name.py
